Description: dry
        ===
        
        Automate and enhance your web development workflow
        
        dry will do for you in one command line `dry build`:
        
        * compile & minify coffee scripts
        * compile & minify sass & css
        * minify js
        * inject minified css/js into html
        * minify html
        
